sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  Client       ->> ShinyServer: user selects a metric and subregion (unit is pra)
  ShinyServer  ->> DuckDB:      SELECT zone_seq, score FROM zone_metric JOIN zone
  DuckDB       ->> ShinyServer: per-Program-Area scores (one row per PA)
  Note over ShinyServer: build a mapgl match_expr paint rule —<br/>column programarea_key,<br/>stops d_pra$fill_color
  ShinyServer  ->> Client:      send fill-color match_expr and layer ids via Shiny proxy
  Client       ->> Caddy:       (once per session) range GET on ply_programareas_2026.pmtiles
  Caddy        ->> Client:      PMTiles vector features (Program Area polygons, keyed by programarea_key)
  Note over Client: mapbox-gl applies the match_expr paint —<br/>values live from DuckDB,<br/>geometry from static PMTiles.<br/>No tile re-render on metric change, only paint updates.
